articles.title: Must watch: Six enduring favourites at Australian Open 2025 - Australian Open
articles.description: Catch Gael Monfils, Victoria Azarenka, Stan Wawrinka, Roberto Bautista Agut, Danielle Collins and Novak Djokovic in action at AO 2025 – some of whom have been competing at Melbourne Park for more than 20 years
articles.content:
Azarenka has reached six AO quarterfinals, three semifinals, and two finals, cementing herself in the top echelon of tournament performers.
